{"tid":1510782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共或動用《緊急法》期待手持美金同午餐肉就有西屌既日子","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:23:25.000Z","uid":13663,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e221660b0a1c63894f3e9e30cd6836b6d755ccdf","tid":1510782,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">緊急法又好, 解放軍又好,200知流浮山刀手又好,戒嚴又好</span>,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924276.jpg&h=0447ef5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924275.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924275.jpg&h=8ac8e8b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i62.photobucket.com/albums/h85/devillam/20110924274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi62.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh85%2Fdevillam%2F20110924274.jpg&h=4662e826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xEpgd5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxEpgd5m.jpg&h=86cbada1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重頭戲 美金就一定係必須啦<br />\n無論任何時候都通用既貨幣<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持美金同午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ebee75272c0ccaa1ac2d7eadca5a41fd02a56b","tid":1510782,"uid":224672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fef55b0e83d2e54e3fcd850fe903a494792875d3","tid":1510782,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"樓主分條女比我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267fcee2c36fa538b16a89f14c373dbbb63cf9e1","tid":1510782,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fef55b0e83d2e54e3fcd850fe903a494792875d3","tid":1510782,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"樓主分條女比我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"換美金啦 屌"},{"pid":"2bae5a4c12011bcdb516c1c43d4b3ad58aa71a45","tid":1510782,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fef55b0e83d2e54e3fcd850fe903a494792875d3","tid":1510782,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:13:10.000Z","msg":"樓主分條女比我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我等買平樓"},{"pid":"d610ed563d